        ,openssh-server
        ,python3-opengl
# authentication:
        ,python3-kerberos
        ,python3-gssapi
# keycloak authentication:
        ,python3-oauthlib
Description: tool to detach/reattach running X programs,
 this is server component allowing you to start sessions


